SUMMARY:Plowman and Cummins are Plowman and Cummins
LOCATION:London
DESCRIPTION:Clown duo Plowman and Cummins present a surreal trip to the hai
 rdressers. Expect bouncy blow-dries\, falling over\, mess\, beauty\, violen
 ce and classical singing. Using absurd visual comedy\, physical theatre and
  splintered narrative\, Plowman and Cummins herald a slapstick revival. The
  salon dissolves into moments of chaos\, danger and silliness as objects\, 
 costumes and bodies morph in and out of reality. Part-clown part-performanc
 e art\, ‘Plowman and Cummins are Plowman and Cummins’ is their debut ho
 ur-long comedy show\, appearing at Brighton Fringe for the very first time.
  For fans of foolishness\, laughing and the feeling you get when you watch 
 someone run for the bus as it drives away.\nMore info: https://comedyatlas.
 app/comedy-atlas/event/plowman-and-cummins-are-plowman-and-cummins/
